      "section": "4 LLMs results on GAIA",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "span_text": "Results. Our evaluation can be found in Figure 4, with more details in Table 4 (Appendix D.1). Our proposed levels of dificulty, loosely defined in terms of number of steps and number of diferent capabilities used, are correlated with the performance of current models, strengthening their validity. While humans excel at all levels, current best LLMs do poorly. Overall, <sup>GAIA</sup> allows to clearly rank capable assistants, while leaving a lot of room for improvement in the coming months and perhaps years.",
      "supports_claim_ids": [],
      "table_id": null,
      "table_screenshot_available": false,
      "title": "GAIA: a benchmark for General AI Assistants"
